author: wn.com
title: Villani: Howard Dean calls for Elizabeth Warren to endorse Hillary Clinton
text: Former Vermont Gov. Howard Dean said he hopes U.S. Sen. Elizabeth Warren will follow his lead in endorsing Hillary Clinton for president, and called the investigation into the former secretary of state over Benghazi a “partisan witch hunt”
